,"body":"정말로 맛있었어~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"episode101-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"코코롱도 상당히 마음에 들어 했었지? 그 빵.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode101-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"아~ 「웃는 얼굴 빵」이야기구만.\n너희가 붙인 이름이니까 책임지고 제대로 불러!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"아까부터 왜 그래, 아리사?\n설마 아리사는 꽃놀이가 즐겁지 않았어??","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode101-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"즐거울 리가 없잖아!\n이쪽은 진이 다 빠졌다! 해롱해롱!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"하지만 아리사 처음에는 별로 말도 없었던 것 같은데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"episode101-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"그러니까 쓸데없이 더 지쳤다고!\n네 녀석들의 이상한 대화에 끼게 되어서!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"……그래도 네 녀석들은 그나마 낫지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"……문제는 그 녀석이야! 그 녀석!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"그 녀석??","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode101-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"뻔하잖아, 츠루마키 코코로 말이야!\n그 녀석, 하는 짓 하나하나 전부 의미를 알 수 없다고!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"뭐야, 그 겁나 거대한 집은!?\n그런 게 진짜 있다니, 보통은 상상도 안 가잖냐!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"진짜 그랬지~! 그런 집에서 살고 있다니\n엄청 놀랐어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode101-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"난 그 검은 옷을 입은 사람들에게 놀랐어.\n끝까지 정체를 알 수 없었지만……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"episode101-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"엥? 코코롱이 말했잖아.\n코코롱이 못해서 곤란해하는 일을\n해 주는 사람들이라고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode101-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"그걸로 이해가 가능한 네가 정말 대단~하다.\n여러모로 존경스러워.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode101-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"조, 존경이라니~ 그러지 마~ 아리사~♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode101-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"re